effect_entries.effect: During strong sunlight, this Pokémon has 1.5× its Special Attack but takes 1/8 of its maximum HP in damage after each turn.
effect_entries.short_effect: Increases Special Attack to 1.5× but costs 1/8 max HP after each turn during strong sunlight.

flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
晴朗天气时，
特攻会提高，
而每回合ＨＰ会减少。

天気が　晴れると
特攻が　上がるが
毎ターン　ＨＰが　減る。

Boosts the Sp. Atk stat in harsh sunlight, but HP
decreases every turn.

Se la luce del sole è intensa, l’Attacco Speciale
aumenta, ma il Pokémon perde PS a ogni turno.

Si hace sol, aumenta su Ataque Especial, pero
pierde PS en cada turno.

Führt bei Sonnenschein in jeder Runde zu
KP-Verlusten, erhöht aber den Spezial-Angriff.

Quand le soleil brille, l’Attaque Spéciale du Pokémon
augmente mais il perd des PV à chaque tour.

effect_entries.effect: When this Pokémon has 1/3 or less of its HP remaining, its fire-type moves inflict 1.5× as much regular damage.
effect_entries.short_effect: Strengthens fire moves to inflict 1.5× damage at 1/3 max HP or less.
